description:
Who will you bow to and worship at Jesus return? What if youve already been deceived? Could you mistake Satan for Christ, and his demons for Jesus disciples? Matt Schanche and MacKenzie Drebit look at Satans horrifying plans for deceiving the whole world and show why Christians are not immune. 

How can you prepare for Satans masterpiece of deception, his counterfeit of the Second Coming? Find out how humanity has been pre-programmed to accept demonic delusions that will sweep the whole world into Satans system of church-state government.


1:55 The coming church-state system which the Bible calls Mystery Babylon.
3:45 Rev 17:5-6. Mystery Babylon, little horn power. What it did before its going to do again.
5:25 The harlots daughters, Protestant denominations.
6:05 Conspiracy theorists missing piece of the puzzle. Bible identifies Protestantism as the source of the image of the beast and the mark of the beast, also source of false miracles.
7:25 Nature of Satans counterfeits. Miracles by the Protestant power will generate global religion.
8:40 Real world examples of how Satan creates his counterfeits. Virgin birth and resurrection story. Zeitgeist  the Jesus story is a knock-off from other cultures.
10:40 Virgin birth and resurrection stories in ancient pagan religions all arose before Jesus was born. Gods plan revealed from the beginning.
12:05 Satans foreknowledge of Christs life and resurrection.
13:10 Pagan empire became Christianized. Counterfeit Christian church: Roman Catholic. Great Controversy p 49-51
14:20 Great Controversy, world and church history. Call AD to get a copy.
15:25 Roman Catholic system, Satans counterfeit. Paganism conquered through the Roman church. Constantine. Satan ruling through the church. Papal supremacy.
18:40 Shape of transition to one world government. French Revolution a pattern for whats to come.
19:55 Miracles will set up for mark of the beast. Counterfeit of Christs miracles. Latter rain of Holy Spirit vs. counterfeit.
21:50 What Jesus did. Two main categories of miracles: healing, raising the dead. False Second Coming.
23:03 Rev 13, second beast, to enforce image of beast through miracle working.
24:23 Satans appearance as Christ.
29:10 Spiritualisms role in deceiving the world. Satan raising the dead.
33:29 Dead loved ones in robes of light. Mans consciousness in death vs. Biblical state of the dead.
35:25 World pre-programmed to accept Satans deceptions; immortality of the soul.
37:23 History of modern-day spiritualism: Fox sisters, haunted houses.
38:41 Doctrine of natural immortality. Spirits not deceased loved ones, but fallen angels. Witch of Endor.
41:53 Apparitions. Trusting our senses vs. trusting Gods Word. Evil spirits posing as apostles, the power that unites church and state. Mass revivals vs. the remnant.
47:40 Revelation 12:9: Satan cast into the earth with his angels. Satan and his demons posing as Christ and the apostles will convert the world. Testing the spirits: the law of God.
50:40 What will happen to the world when Christ returns. No fixing this world.
52:20 The elect. Read the will of God, hear it, do it. Aligning ourselves with Gods character. How to be Gods remnant.
55:00 The world teeming with devils. Revelation 18:2.
56:40 Every foul spirit and every hateful bird. One taken, one left. Matthew 24:40-41.
58:58 GC 591. Communications with the dead, evil spirits.
59:58 Sunday observance to be enforced. Elijah a type of the remnant at the end of time. Climate and Sunday.
1:04:10 The whole world to hate the remnant at the end. Church and state in view now. Mark of the beast vs. seal of God.
